<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Agent Status Update</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2563eb;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #2563eb;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #1d4ed8;
        }
        .status-change {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .status-active {
            background-color: #f0fdf4;
            border-color: #10b981;
            color: #065f46;
        }
        .status-inactive {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border-color: #ef4444;
            color: #7f1d1d;
        }
        .status-away {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            border-color: #f59e0b;
            color: #78350f;
        }
        .status-busy {
            background-color: #fdf2f8;
            border-color: #ec4899;
            color: #831843;
        }
        .agent-info {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .info-row:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4b5563;
        }
        .info-value {
            color: #1f2937;
        }
        .notification-badge {
            background-color: #6366f1;
            color: white;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .impact-notice {
            background-color: #f0f9ff;
            border: 1px solid #0ea5e9;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">AIgentable</div>
            <div class="notification-badge">Status Update</div>
            <h1 class="title">Agent Status Changed</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello Team,</p>
            
            <p>An agent's status has been updated in your AIgentable workspace. Please review the details below:</p>
            
            <div class="agent-info">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1f2937;">ðŸ‘¤ Agent Information</h3>
                
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Agent Name:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{agentName}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Agent ID:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">#{{agentId}}</span>
                </div>
                
                {{#if updatedBy}}
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Updated By:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{updatedBy}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Updated At:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{updatedAt}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="status-change status-{{newStatus}}">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">ðŸ“Š Status Change</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 18px; margin: 10px 0;">
                    <strong>{{previousStatus}}</strong> â†’ <strong>{{newStatus}}</strong>
                </p>
                {{#if statusReason}}
                <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><em>Reason: {{statusReason}}</em></p>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            {{#if impactDescription}}
            <div class="impact-notice">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #0369a1;">ðŸ“‹ Impact Assessment</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">{{impactDescription}}</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">View Dashboard</a>
            </div>
            
            <p><strong>ðŸ“ˆ Status Definitions:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Active:</strong> Agent is online and available for new conversations</li>
                <li><strong>Away:</strong> Agent is temporarily unavailable but may return soon</li>
                <li><strong>Busy:</strong> Agent is handling maximum capacity of conversations</li>
                <li><strong>Inactive:</strong> Agent is offline and not available for new assignments</li>
            </ul>
            
            {{#if activeConversations}}
            <p><strong>Current Active Conversations:</strong> {{activeConversations}}</p>
            {{/if}}
            
            <p>This status change may affect conversation routing and team capacity. Please review your team's availability and adjust assignments if necessary.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>AIgentable Management System</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This notification was sent because an agent status was updated in your workspace.</p>
            <p>You can manage notification preferences for status changes in your admin settings.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>